data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this stunning 2-story, 6-bedroom, 3-bath home that's the epitome of modern living. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the fresh paint and open floor plan that seamlessly combines comfort and style. The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, featuring a gas range, stainless steel appliances, and elegant granite countertops - a dream for any culinary enthusiast. The upper level primary suite is nothing short of expansive, offering a serene retreat with its en-suite bathroom, a luxurious walk-in closet, and a separate sitting/changing room. On the main level, two additional rooms provide versatility, perfect for guest bedrooms, a home office, or even a personal gym, catering to your ever-evolving needs. The upper-level bonus/game room is a wonderful space to unwind, entertain, or create cherished memories with family and friends. As you step outside, you'll be greeted by a backyard oasis, ready for your creative landscaping ideas, outdoor gatherings, or simply enjoying the open space. This move-in-ready home is not only a gem on its own but also situated in a community that boasts two inviting pools and a playground - an extension of your living space for endless fun and relaxation. Furthermore, it's blocks away from the elementary school which is ideal for your morning walk and its proximity to I-35 makes commuting to Austin or San Antonio a breeze, offering convenience that's hard to beat. Do not miss out on this wonderful opportunity! Welcome home!
